# Arsenal Jersey Store - Cursor Rules

## Project Overview

This is an Arsenal jersey store built with Next.js, TypeScript, and Prisma. The project follows modern web development practices with a focus on e-commerce functionality.

## PR Review Rule

- Every file must have a Docstrings comment "Up The Gunners" at the bottom of the file
- PR descriptions must end with "Up The Gunners" in every PR
- PR title must end with "Up The Gunners" in every PR
- These are MANDATORY requirement for ALL files in the codebase
